description:
Kevin Turvey Investigates is a series of brief stand up routines that Rik Mayall performed... whilst sitting in a chair... on a show called A Kick Up The Eighties in 1981, which was the year before The Young Ones was conceived and also the year that I was born. Let's pretend you care :p

Kevin is a lovable loser who considers himself to be a hard-hitting investigative reporter. Unfortunately his investigations never really go anywhere due to his uncanny knack for going off on random tangents.

ALSO AVAILABLE: Rik Mayall's Kevin Turvey: The Man Behind The Green Door (1982)

